        <skos:example xml:lang="en">For a BreakdownElement there is a textual document assigned, explaining the functionality, size, and other characteristics by a DocumentAssignment with role &apos;description&apos;. Another document, representing the specification of the ProductClass, in which the BreakdownElement is used, is also assigned to the same BreakdownElement by a DocumentAssignment with role &apos;additional information&apos;.</skos:example>
