        <skos:changeNote>[2021-07-30] Initial definition.</skos:changeNote>
        <skos:example xml:lang="en">A requirement on the performance of a catalytic converter in a car may be traced from a more general emissions requirement.</skos:example>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">tracing relationship</skos:prefLabel>
